The Albena Estate is located on the eastern end of [[Calden]]. Constructed during the last half of  [[The Age of War]], the estate is a lagre stately home, and several square kilometres worth of grounds and orchards. The gardens of the Albena Estate are renound in [[Edion|The Realm of Edion]] for their beauty and elegance. Estate staff is carefully hand chosen by [[Duchess Ivania Albena]] and none other than staff and personal guests of the Albena family are allowed into the Estate.